{
  "texts": [
    "Aspect tags can be single words or phrases.",
    "Applying document attention to 𝑉𝑒𝑣𝑡𝑜𝑟 -𝐷 yields the result represented by 𝑉𝑒𝑣𝑡𝑜𝑟 -𝑆.",
    "To ensure the model focuses on the most relevant features for a given aspect, we perform cross-attention feature extraction between comment features and aspect tag word features.",
    "We denote the result of this cross-attention as 𝑉𝑒𝑣𝑡𝑜𝑟 -𝑅, which is then concatenated with 𝑉𝑒𝑣𝑡𝑜𝑟 -𝑆.",
    "Finally, we can predict the sentiment polarity of the given aspect category text through a classification layer consisting of fully connected layers and softmax."
  ]
}